   <description>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">Payment to German RC covering the 4th instalment on the original GAD (&#xC2;&#xA3;120,000) plus an agreed budget extension of &#xC2;&#xA3;49,780
The budget extension relates to the following:

Costs relating to development of a hospital information system to be piloted in GRC-supported clinics (NB/ most associated costs for this will be included in the new phase of support from Feb 2021 onwards)
Salary support to additional medical staff
Increases in budget lines for medical equipment (reflecting price increases in Yemen following COVID-19.

&#xC2;&#xA0;
The extension has been agreed upon consultation with relevant advisors and approval of the &quot;Decision to amend&quot; on the Hajjah Project page. A signed Grant Addendum is also attached reflecting the increased total amount.&#xC2;&#xA0;
&#xC2;</narrative>
   </description>
